channel.title: [PI] Changing Teleports
channel.description: I know it sounds stupid but I am having real problems changing one of the skilling teleports. The original coords are at 2813, 3436 so i gave them a search and changed them to what I wanted them to be (3103, 3096). But when I compile and open the server it doesn't change, and when i click the teleport it goes to the original location. Something im missing out? help!
